data.description: Come see one of the largest floor plans offered in Valley Ranch! Two stories, 5 bedrooms, 3 and a half bath, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, white subway tile backsplash, and more. Valley Ranch has arguably the best HOA amenities in the area. Complete with a pool and water park style amenities, fishing ponds, workout center, tennis courts, basketball courts and great park for kids. Schools for kids of all ages are close in proximity to the home. The home was built in 2022 so there is a transferable warranty from the builder for several more months and also a 10 year transferable warranty with a little over 8 years remaining for the new owner of this home. Call today to schedule your showing!
